etsysJumboEthernetFrameMIB.name: etsysJumboEthernetFrameMIB

revisions.description: Changed the per port enable status to a per port administrative and operational status.

etsysJumboEthernetFrameMIB.contactinfo: Postal: Enterasys Networks 35 Industrial Way, P.O. Box 5005 Rochester, NH 03867-0505 Phone: +1 603 332 9400 E-mail: support@enterasys.com WWW: http://www.enterasys.com
etsysJumboEthernetFrameMIB.description: This MIB module defines a portion of the SNMP MIB under the Enterasys Networks enterprise OID pertaining to jumbo Ethernet frames.

etsysJumboEnetFrameTable.name: etsysJumboEnetFrameTable
etsysJumboEnetFrameTable.description: A list of entries for interfaces that have support for jumbo Ethernet frames.

etsysJumboEnetFrameEntry.name: etsysJumboEnetFrameEntry
etsysJumboEnetFrameEntry.description: An entry containing management information applicable to a particular interface that has support for jumbo Ethernet frames.

etsysJumboEnetFrameEnable.name: etsysJumboEnetFrameEnable
etsysJumboEnetFrameEnable.description: The enabled/disabled status of the passing of jumbo Ethernet frames on the interface.

etsysJumboEnetFrameMtu.name: etsysJumboEnetFrameMtu
etsysJumboEnetFrameMtu.description: The MTU for this interface when etsysJumboEnetFrameEnable is enabled. The managed entity will reflect this value in ifMtu when the passing of jumbo frames is enabled on this interface.

etsysJumboEnetFrameAdminStatus.name: etsysJumboEnetFrameAdminStatus
etsysJumboEnetFrameAdminStatus.description: The administrative enabled/disabled status for the passing of jumbo Ethernet frames on this interface.

etsysJumboEnetFrameOperStatus.name: etsysJumboEnetFrameOperStatus
etsysJumboEnetFrameOperStatus.description: The operational status of the passing of jumbo Ethernet frames on this interface.

etsysJumboEnetFrameControlGroup.name: etsysJumboEnetFrameControlGroup
etsysJumboEnetFrameControlGroup.description: A collection of objects relating to per interface Jumbo Ethernet frame support.

etsysJumboEnetFrameControlGroup2.name: etsysJumboEnetFrameControlGroup2
etsysJumboEnetFrameControlGroup2.description: A collection of objects relating to per interface Jumbo Ethernet frame support.

etsysJumboEnetFrameCompliance.name: etsysJumboEnetFrameCompliance
etsysJumboEnetFrameCompliance.description: The compliance statement for devices that support the Enterasys Jumbo Ethernet Frame MIB.

etsysJumboEnetFrameCompliance2.name: etsysJumboEnetFrameCompliance2
etsysJumboEnetFrameCompliance2.description: The compliance statement for devices that support the Enterasys Jumbo Ethernet Frame MIB.
